Bundled browser dependencies
============================

The Registry UI vendors a small number of browser-side dependencies so the
local UI can run without a JavaScript package installation step.

- Cytoscape.js
  - File: octopus_registry/ui/vendor/cytoscape.umd.js
  - License: MIT
  - Copyright: The Cytoscape Consortium

- Eclipse Layout Kernel for JavaScript
  - File: octopus_registry/ui/vendor/elk.bundled.js
  - License: Eclipse Public License 2.0
  - Copyright: Kiel University and others

- Fuse.js
  - File: octopus_registry/ui/vendor/fuse.min.js
  - License: Apache License 2.0
  - Copyright: Kiro Risk

- morphdom
  - File: octopus_registry/ui/vendor/morphdom.min.js
  - License: MIT

The files octopus_registry/ui/vendor/purify.min.js and
octopus_registry/ui/vendor/marked.min.js are local minimal compatibility
implementations for the Registry UI sanitizer and Markdown-rendering surfaces.
They are not full upstream DOMPurify or marked.js distributions.
